        11242
      ],
      "content": "The <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Azure Active Directory Application Gallery<ept id=\"p1\">](http://azure.microsoft.com/marketplace/active-directory/all/)</ept> provides a listing of applications that are known to support a form of single sign-on with Azure Active Directory."
