      "content": "Azure AD supports automatic provisioning and de-provisioning for all “Featured” apps in the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Azure Active Directory Application Gallery<ept id=\"p1\">](http://azure.microsoft.com/marketplace/active-directory/all/)</ept>."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
