    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Add an unlisted app you are using<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> - Use the Custom category in the app gallery within the Azure management portal to connect an unlisted application that your organization is using.",
      "pos": [
        12164,
        12349
      ]
    },
    {
