      "pos": [
        12350,
        12498
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For more details, see this article on <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>adding your own application<ept id=\"p1\">](http://blogs.technet.com/b/ad/archive/2015/06/17/bring-your-own-app-with-azure-ad-self-service-saml-configuration-gt-now-in-preview.aspx)</ept>.",
